Project Overview
This project focuses on improving supply chain visibility using Power BI by analyzing inventory performance and delivery efficiency. The dashboard provides insights into inventory turnover, identification of slow/fast-moving products, and delivery performance metrics.
Project Structure
Supply_Chain_Visibility_Optimization/
└── Milestone 2/
